019package com.plotsquared.core.inject.factory;
020
021import com.google.inject.assistedinject.Assisted;
022import com.plotsquared.core.queue.ChunkCoordinator;
023import com.plotsquared.core.queue.subscriber.ProgressSubscriber;
024import com.sk89q.worldedit.math.BlockVector2;
025import com.sk89q.worldedit.world.World;
026import org.checkerframework.checker.nullness.qual.NonNull;
027
028import java.util.Collection;
029import java.util.function.Consumer;
030
031public interface ChunkCoordinatorFactory {
032
033    @NonNull ChunkCoordinator create(
034            final long maxIterationTime,
035            final int initialBatchSize,
036            final @NonNull Consumer<BlockVector2> chunkConsumer,
037            final @NonNull World world,
038            final @NonNull Collection<BlockVector2> requestedChunks,
039            final @NonNull Runnable whenDone,
040            final @NonNull Consumer<Throwable> throwableConsumer,
041            @Assisted("unloadAfter") final boolean unloadAfter,
042            final @NonNull Collection<ProgressSubscriber> progressSubscribers,
043            @Assisted("forceSync") final boolean forceSync
044    );
045
046}
